msg.msgText: Destination mapping rule {0}. Queue manager connection {1}. Unable to subscribe to WebSphere MQ topic {2}. Subscription name {3}. Subscription exists with topic string ending {4}.

msgExplanation.p: A failure occurred while attempting to subscribe to a WebSphere MQ topic as a subscription with the same name exists with a different topic string.

msgUserResponse.p: Delete the subscription from the WebSphere MQ queue manager if it is no longer required.
